  {"word":"nutrient","pos":"n","ja":"栄養素","level":5,"cat":"academic","ipa":"/ˈnuːtriənt/","ex":"Sensors monitor nutrient levels in the hydroponic system.","exJa":"センサーは水耕システムの栄養素レベルを監視する。","collocations":["essential nutrient","nutrient level"],"synonyms":["nourishment"],"distractorHint":["中立の","中和する","毒素"]},
