  {"word":"obscure","pos":"adj","ja":"不明瞭な、あいまいな","level":5,"cat":"academic","ipa":"/əbˈskjʊr/","ex":"The cause of the failure remains obscure to engineers.","exJa":"故障の原因は技術者にとって依然不明瞭である。","collocations":["remain obscure","obscure reference"],"synonyms":["unclear","vague"],"distractorHint":["明確な","観察する","賛成する"]},
  {"word":"obsolete","pos":"adj","ja":"廃れた、旧式の","level":5,"cat":"academic","ipa":"/ˌɑːbsəˈliːt/","ex":"That old communication protocol is now considered completely obsolete.","exJa":"その古い通信プロトコルは今では完全に旧式とみなされている。","collocations":["become obsolete","obsolete technology"],"synonyms":["outdated","outmoded"],"distractorHint":["絶対的な","解消する","最新の"]},
