  {"word":"obvious","pos":"adj","ja":"明白な","level":5,"cat":"academic","ipa":"/ˈɑːbviəs/","ex":"It is obvious that the sensor needs recalibration.","exJa":"センサーの再調整が必要なのは明白である。","collocations":["obvious reason","painfully obvious"],"synonyms":["evident","clear"],"distractorHint":["不明瞭な","従順な","邪魔な"]},
