  {"word":"occur","pos":"v","ja":"起こる、生じる","level":5,"cat":"academic","ipa":"/əˈkɜːr/","ex":"Overheating tends to occur under heavy computational load.","exJa":"過熱は計算負荷が高い時に発生しやすい。","collocations":["occur frequently","an error occurs"],"synonyms":["happen","arise"],"distractorHint":["占める","防ぐ","繰り返す"]},
  {"word":"offset","pos":"v","ja":"相殺する","level":5,"cat":"academic","ipa":"/ˌɒfˈset/","ex":"Higher material costs were offset by lower labor costs.","exJa":"材料費の増加は人件費の低下によって相殺された。","collocations":["offset the cost","offset emissions"],"synonyms":["counterbalance","compensate for"],"distractorHint":["上書きする","増加させる","設定する"]},
