  {"word":"participate","pos":"v","ja":"参加する","level":5,"cat":"academic","ipa":"/pɑːrˈtɪsɪpeɪt/","ex":"All members were encouraged to participate in the discussion.","exJa":"全員が議論に参加するよう促された。","collocations":["participate in","actively participate"],"synonyms":["take part","engage"],"distractorHint":["予期する","任命する","脱退する"]},
