  {"word":"perception","pos":"n","ja":"知覚、認識","level":5,"cat":"academic","ipa":"/pərˈsepʃən/","ex":"Public perception of the technology shifted after the demo.","exJa":"そのデモの後、技術に対する社会の認識が変わった。","collocations":["public perception","shape perception"],"synonyms":["awareness","insight"],"distractorHint":["受容","欺瞞","誤解"]},
  {"word":"periodic","pos":"adj","ja":"周期的な","level":5,"cat":"academic","ipa":"/ˌpɪriˈɑːdɪk/","ex":"The sensor sends periodic updates every ten seconds.","exJa":"そのセンサーは10秒ごとに周期的な更新を送る。","collocations":["periodic update","periodic inspection"],"synonyms":["regular","cyclical"],"distractorHint":["永久的な","不規則な","危険な"]},
  {"word":"permanent","pos":"adj","ja":"永久的な","level":5,"cat":"academic","ipa":"/ˈpɜːrmənənt/","ex":"The vibration caused permanent damage to the circuit board.","exJa":"その振動は基板に永久的な損傷を与えた。","collocations":["permanent damage","permanent solution"],"synonyms":["lasting","enduring"],"distractorHint":["一時的な","周期的な","許可された"]},
