  {"word":"perspective","pos":"n","ja":"視点、観点","level":5,"cat":"academic","ipa":"/pərˈspektɪv/","ex":"From an engineering perspective, the design is inefficient.","exJa":"工学的な観点から見ると、その設計は非効率である。","collocations":["from a ... perspective","broader perspective"],"synonyms":["viewpoint","standpoint"],"distractorHint":["見通し","側面","疑い"]},
  {"word":"phase","pos":"n","ja":"段階、フェーズ","level":5,"cat":"academic","ipa":"/feɪz/","ex":"The project entered its final testing phase last month.","exJa":"プロジェクトは先月最終試験段階に入った。","collocations":["initial phase","phase out"],"synonyms":["stage","period"],"distractorHint":["顔","位置","急激な変化"]},
