  {"word":"portion","pos":"n","ja":"部分、割合","level":5,"cat":"academic","ipa":"/ˈpɔːrʃən/","ex":"A large portion of the budget went to sensor development.","exJa":"予算の大部分がセンサー開発に使われた。","collocations":["a portion of","allocate a portion"],"synonyms":["part","share"],"distractorHint":["比率","全体","肖像"]},
